videos.description: Omar Payne finishes Scottie Lewis' missed layup with a two-handed putback dunk.
videos.headline: Payne skies for putback dunk

videos.description: Andrew Nembhard lobs the inbounds pass to Keyontae Johnson, who soars through the lane and throws down a huge dunk.
videos.headline: Gators execute inbounds alley-oop slam

videos.description: Devin Vassell goes way up for Trent Forrest's inbounds pass and throws down a monster two-handed slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Vassell throws down alley-oop dunk off the inbounds) 2019/11/10

videos.headline: Vassell throws down alley-oop dunk off the inbounds

videos.description: Trent Forrest comes up with the steal, then feeds Devin Vassell, who throws it down on the other end.
videos.headline: Vassell throws down fast-break dunk

videos.description: Keyontae Johnson drives baseline and gets partially blocked by Devin Vassell, but he holds on for the two-hand flush.

videos.description: Patrick Williams gets behind the Gators' defense and skies for a huge alley-oop slam.
videos.headline: Williams skies for alley-oop slam
